      "id": 20,
      "options": {
        "code": {
          "language": "plaintext",
          "showLineNumbers": false,
          "showMiniMap": false
        },
        "content": "## Alert Management Quick Reference\n\n### Access Points\n| Service | URL | Purpose |\n|---------|-----|--------|\n| **Grafana Alerting** | [grafana.stx.local:30090/alerting](http://23.92.79.2:30090/alerting) | Configure Grafana alerts |\n| **Alertmanager** | [alertmanager.stx.local:30093](http://23.92.79.2:30093) | View/silence alerts |\n| **Prometheus Alerts** | [prometheus.stx.local:30091/alerts](http://23.92.79.2:30091/alerts) | View Prometheus alert rules |\n\n### Common Actions\n\n#### Create a Silence\n```bash\namtool silence add \\\n  --alertmanager.url=http://23.92.79.2:30093 \\\n  --author=\"your-name\" \\\n  --comment=\"Reason for silence\" \\\n  --duration=\"2h\" \\\n  alertname=\"AlertName\"\n```\n\n#### List Active Silences\n```bash\namtool silence query --alertmanager.url=http://23.92.79.2:30093\n```\n\n#### Expire a Silence\n```bash\namtool silence expire --alertmanager.url=http://23.92.79.2:30093 <silence-id>\n```\n\n#### Check Alert Rules\n```bash\ncurl -s http://23.92.79.2:30091/api/v1/rules | jq '.data.groups[].rules[] | {name: .name, state: .state}'\n```\n\n### Severity Levels\n- 🔴 **Critical**: Immediate response required (< 5 min)\n- 🟠 **Warning**: Response within 30 minutes\n- 🔵 **Info**: Review during next business day\n\n### Escalation Contacts\n- **Platform Team**: #platform-alerts (Slack)\n- **On-Call**: PagerDuty escalation policy\n- **Email**: oncall@example.com",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "10.0.0",
      "title": "Alert Management Guide",
      "type": "text"
    }
